IZE}\" /><br />\n而<strong>005支cam嘅57秒唔見咗</strong>。呢啲咁technical 嘅嘢真係唔知。會唔會係剪過片定純粹CCTV出咗問題。我唔識upload video or gif，麻煩大家自己睇返。<br />\n<br />\n之後就係<strong>18:37:48 同18:38:18唔對位</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eecEevq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeecEevq.jpg&h=6242d3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NH43Gau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNH43Gau.jpg&h=4d7b62c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢行得咁smooth點解可以差成30秒<br />\n一係個CCTV啲時間有問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"之後18:38:33-18:42:43喺第九段片唔見人，唔知做乜，<strong>要補返支cam</strong><br />\n<br />\n18:42:48喺返度，左手拎住鑰匙<br />\n<br />\n18:43:09唔搭lift改行樓梯去7樓<br />\n18:43:28到七樓用咗20秒係合理，<strong>但呢一秒條片有停滯咗</strong> <br />\n<br />\n到39秒又停<br />\n<br />\n到49秒出咗個人又停，而格仔打打下又唔打，好似鼓勵您查落去咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/um0eNTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fum0eNTQ.jpg&h=71460b9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3frp97a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3frp97a.jpg&h=d8bb3960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到18:43:55 佢唔係去樓梯方向，<strong>要補返支Cam</strong><br />\n<br />\n喺18:44:55-56唔知點解突然加速<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XD1d3s2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXD1d3s2.jpg&h=de5b97b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n類似情況有出現喺<br />\n45:06；45:15；45:26；45:39；45:51；45:59<br />\n去到18:46:02<strong>喺返九樓</strong><br />\n之間差咗兩分鐘唔知佢做過乜<br />\n18:46:12按完lift又走咗唔搭<br />\n同時間又出現返嗰個男仔<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biNXLJc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiNXLJc.jpg&h=3b1abe8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用處睇下會唔會聯絡到個男仔，我覺得啲都想俾呢啲方向我哋，又唔完全遮曬所有嘢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:12:03.000Z","msg":"跟住又行到去類似common area<br />\n18:47:08 由九樓到到達七樓呢個地方少於一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n之後出現一個男人打打下格仔又唔打<br />\n另一條又會見到佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JiqqUDf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJiqqUDf.jpg&h=05d2bf97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7ns7Yg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7ns7Yg.jpg&h=20ecd818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住出現兩個女仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uGsYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uGsYN.jpg&h=999704a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地本來係分開咗行，去到之後段片佢哋會去返同一個地點見面<br />\n去到片尾，兩個女仔出埋出門口，兩個向左走，一個向右走，有冇可能之後兩分鐘相遇，呢個要問返學生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SiVZeDO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSiVZeDO.jpg&h=8ae8bd1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而佢係跟住男人行，好似帶領佢去lift咁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBDDvc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBDDvc8.jpg&h=ac71caeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住佢又按lift。<br />\n去到18:50:05離開<br />\n<br />\n呢度又係我覺得奇怪嘅位黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emVB1kt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemVB1kt.jpg&h=3860d96b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GaYPBTP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGaYPBTP.jpg&h=9b1463aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一個gesture但又唔同時間。<br />\n另一個係18:50:12<br />\n佢跟住一群打格仔嘅人向前轉左走，<br />\n去到18:50:47調返轉走。<br />\n<br />\n佢用4分鐘去咗另一個地方，又有個途人，白色衫，鞋係白底黑色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qqnHWWR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqqnHWWR.jpg&h=b2ac4163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n18:56:35 去到一樓由七樓到一樓赤腳行樓梯，有冇可能？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUQB1ot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUQB1ot.jpg&h=9e598531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18:59:20喺街 3分鐘嘅時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjEbQgK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjEbQgK.jpg&h=a9a9d1de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02f76338c660082d0cbdcc935b4edbe0a9acca49","tid":1659093,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc13f2d0ec59d4eddf47717b28dedf5ce5038c09","tid":1659093,"uid":284745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"447e064b61e5f410194e38ffd33255fc57b4f63f","tid":1659093,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:06:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以開集中po討論陳彥霖事件？<br />\n成個熱門都係左幾日，係咪唔洗討論其他野？<br />\n見到既手足幫手copy呢句留言洗版式回應<br />\n推到有集中po為止"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:09:01.000Z","msg":"唔係好明  我照放咗先 您幫幫手"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:16:52.000Z","msg":"即係想大家淨係用集中po討論<br />\n有大事要宣布先開翻個po講<br />\n咁就避免熱門全部都係查案po冇行動po既現象<br />\n利申支持查案，但唔係全神貫注咁查"},{"pid":"f5828ee1954fa20d6882dba42af1817b6b655f75","tid":1659093,"uid":284745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f76338c660082d0cbdcc935b4edbe0a9acca49","tid":1659093,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc13f2d0ec59d4eddf47717b28dedf5ce5038c09","tid":1659093,"uid":284745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"447e064b61e5f410194e38ffd33255fc57b4f63f","tid":1659093,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:06:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以開集中po討論陳彥霖事件？<br />\n成個熱門都係左幾日，係咪唔洗討論其他野？<br />\n見到既手足幫手copy呢句留言洗版式回應<br />\n推到有集中po為止"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:09:01.000Z","msg":"唔係好明  我照放咗先 您幫幫手"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:16:52.000Z","msg":"即係想大家淨係用集中po討論<br />\n有大事要宣布先開翻個po講<br />\n咁就避免熱門全部都係查案po冇行動po既現象<br />\n利申支持查案，但唔係全神貫注咁查"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:26:51.000Z","msg":"更新返，有圖重覆咗<br />\n呢度又係我覺得奇怪嘅位黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emVB1kt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemVB1kt.jpg&h=3860d96b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xKWamDz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKWamDz.jpg&h=95829